  "Topic": "Europe",
  "Title": "Eucharistic Chain 2025: The Prayer of the Church of Europe for Ukraine and the Holy Land During Lent",
  "Annotation": "The European Bishops Celebrated Holy Mass for 40 Consecutive Days to invoke Peace",
  "Content": "<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">From Ash Wednesday and throughout the Lenten Season, the Bishops’ Conferences of Europe celebrated Holy Mass to invoke a just and sustainable peace, especially for Ukraine and the Holy Land.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Lenten initiative, called the “<em>Eucharistic Chain</em>”, involved all 39 members of the CCEE, who, through the Eucharistic celebration, surrounded the entire European Continent with the embrace of the Church, as a real sign of communion, hope and faith in the invincible power of the Eucharist to implore from God the end of the war and the gift of true peace.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Please find below a photo gallery with some images from the celebrations sent by the communication offices of the Bishops’ Conferences.</p>\n</div><div class=\"rl-gallery-item\"><a href=\"https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/491756797_645290471809086_9112629757838143646_n.jpg\" title=\"\" data-rl_title=\"\" class=\"rl-gallery-link swipebox\" data-rl_caption=\"\" data-rel=\"lightbox-gallery-1\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/491756797_645290471809086_9112629757838143646_n-380x253.jpg\" width=\"380\" height=\"253\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div class=\"rl-gallery-item\"><a href=\"https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/491042158_645290548475745_1813652239617664553_n.jpg\" title=\"\" data-rl_title=\"\" class=\"rl-gallery-link swipebox\" data-rl_caption=\"\" data-rel=\"lightbox-gallery-1\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/491042158_645290548475745_1813652239617664553_n-380x253.jpg\" width=\"380\" height=\"253\" alt=\"\"></a></div><div class=\"rl-gallery-item\"><a href=\"https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/490833324_645290551809078_3713043919315956422_n.jpg\" title=\"\" data-rl_title=\"\" class=\"rl-gallery-link swipebox\" data-rl_caption=\"\